		{"id":"dec_label","type":"text","x":-400,"y":200,"width":170,"height":25,"text":"## 9项待决决策"},
		{"id":"dec_detail","type":"text","x":-400,"y":240,"width":420,"height":80,"text":"① 影子输出(A/B/C) → 推荐B(nu→DA)\n② Motor分化 → 推荐C(竞争抑制)\n③ P精度 → 推荐A(保持现状)\n④ 分割定理 → 推荐C(理论)\n⑤ 振荡验证 → 推荐B(调功率)\n⑥ 递归深度 → 2层\n⑦ 运动势 → dK/dt\n⑧ 影子本体 → 抽象\n⑨ 影子生长 → 不生长"},
		{"id":"dec1_a","type":"text","x":160,"y":200,"width":140,"height":35,"text":"⬜ 1B: nu→DA\n推荐·待决","color":"4"},
		{"id":"dec1_b","type":"text","x":160,"y":250,"width":140,"height":35,"text":"⏸️ 1A: 反哺主线\n推迟","color":"5"},
		{"id":"dec1_c","type":"text","x":160,"y":300,"width":140,"height":35,"text":"❌ 1C: 不连接\n不推荐"},
